Auto Reputation Watch

================================================================================
Description

A simple addon that switches the currently watched reputation whenever you gain
reputation in another faction.

================================================================================
Installation

Install the addon by copying the folder to your wow\interface\addons folder. The
addon is intended to work without configuration, so nothing else is needed.
However, there are few settings that can be changed in game.

For in game configuration, use "/arw" or "/autoreputationwatch" to see possible
commands.

